CatDescriptText: David L. Lawrence was Mayor of the City of Pittsburgh 1946-1959, Governor of Pennsylvania 1959-1963, and he died in 1966.
TitMainTitle: Woman, and four men, including David L. Lawrence on left, and one second from left wearing double breasted suit, small lapel pin, and tie with striped V pattern, standing in interior with arabesque patterned wallpaper and men's room in background
